🚀 ASSIGNMENT 3: MAVEN (CLEAR STEPS)
🔹 Step 1: Create Project Folder
In VS Code → create new folder project
🔹 Step 2: Create Files

Inside project create:

👉 pom.xml
👉 src/main/java/com/example/App.java
👉 src/test/java/com/example/AppTest.java

🔹 Step 3: Write Java Code

👉 Open App.java:

public class App {
    public static String grade(int marks){
        if(marks>90) return "A";
        else return "B";
    }
}

👉 Save file

🔹 Step 4: Run Maven Commands

👉 Open terminal:

mvn compile
mvn test
mvn clean install
🔹 Step 5: Jenkins Pipeline
Open Jenkins
Click New Item
Select Pipeline
Click OK

👉 Paste:

pipeline {
    agent any
    stages {
        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                bat 'mvn clean install'
            }
        }
    }
}
Click Save
Click Build Now
